                "href": "/profile/Sujit-Kumar-Mahato"
            },
            "answer_text": "First of all, don't make it a matter of Do or Die.. Option 1Pros1. Enough rest time.2. Will be able to concentrate on school syllabus.3. May perform well in your 12th as well ( as per your confidence mentioned ) Cons1. No Mock Tests2. No comparison against other students.3. May miss a few short-cut methods for particular set of questions. Option 2Pros1. Detailed guidance for entrance exams2. A lot of mock tests3. Will be able to find your weak spots Cons1. May not focus on your 12th2. Extra mental pressure of following the coaching schedule3. Will waste time in travelling school-home-coaching. No one will ever be able to fit into your shoes.You are the master of your life. You are the captain. The Final Decision will always be yours.Good Luck ",
